cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_carrierBandwidth to 1000 exceeds the valid range for downlink carrier bandwidth, causing configuration validation errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_carrierBandwidth 設定為 1000 超過下行載波頻寬的有效範圍，會導致配置驗證錯誤。
